                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-1" style="color: #0A2540;">
                    Ruben Liquenson
                  </h3>
                  <p class="text-sm font-semibold mb-1" style="color: #1E6FFF;">
                    DevOps Engineer | Cloud Engineer | AWS | Kubernetes |
                    Terraform | GitOps
